<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Q &amp; A — Justin &amp; Jen</title>
  <style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Domine:wght@400;700&family=Quicksand:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');

:root {
  --text: #212121;
  --primary: #444444;
  --surface: #fff;
  --link-color: #007bbd;
  --accent-bg: #f7f5f2;
  --border: #e0dcd7;
  --font-heading: 'Domine', serif;
  --font-body: 'Quicksand', sans-serif;
  --button-radius: 12px;
  --max-width: 800px;
}

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  color: var(--text);
  background: var(--surface);
  line-height: 1.7;
  font-size: 16px;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}

a { color: var(--link-color); text-decoration: none; }
a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }

/* ── NAV ── */
.site-header {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  height: 60px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
}

.nav-inner {
  width: 100%; max-width: 1100px;
  padding: 0 20px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
}

.nav-logo {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--text); text-decoration: none;
}

.hamburger {
  background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px;
  padding: 8px;
}
.hamburger span {
  display: block; width: 24px; height: 2px;
  background: var(--text); transition: 0.3s;
}
.hamburger.active span:nth-child(1) { transform: rotate(45deg) translate(5px, 5px); }
.hamburger.active span:nth-child(2) { opacity: 0; }
.hamburger.active span:nth-child(3) { transform: rotate(-45deg) translate(5px, -5px); }

.nav-menu {
  position: fixed; top: 60px; right: -300px;
  width: 280px; height: calc(100vh - 60px);
  background: var(--surface);
  border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
  transition: right 0.3s ease;
  overflow-y: auto;
  list-style: none;
  padding: 20px 0;
}
.nav-menu.open { right: 0; }

.nav-menu li a {
  display: block; padding: 14px 28px;
  color: var(--text); font-weight: 500;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  transition: background 0.2s;
}
.nav-menu li a:hover { background: var(--accent-bg); text-decoration: none; }
.nav-menu li a.active { font-weight: 700; color: var(--link-color); }

.nav-overlay {
  display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); z-index: 99;
}
.nav-overlay.show { display: block; }

/* ── HERO ── */
.hero {
  position: relative;
  height: 85vh; min-height: 500px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  text-align: center; color: #fff;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-top: 60px;
}
.hero-img {
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  width: 100%; height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
}
.hero-overlay {
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.25) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.45) 100%);
}
.hero-content {
  position: relative; z-index: 2;
  padding: 20px;
}
.hero h1 {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}
.hero .subtitle {
  font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem);
  font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.hero .location {
  font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2vw, 1.1rem);
  font-weight: 300;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

/* ── PAGE HERO (inner pages) ── */
.page-hero {
  position: relative;
  height: 45vh; min-height: 300px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  text-align: center; color: #fff;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-top: 60px;
}
.page-hero .hero-img,
.page-hero .hero-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; }
.page-hero .hero-img { object-fit: cover; }
.page-hero .hero-overlay {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.2) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.5) 100%);
}
.page-hero h1 {
  position: relative; z-index: 2;
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
  text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}

/* ── CONTENT ── */
.content {
  max-width: var(--max-width);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 60px 24px 120px;
}

.section { margin-bottom: 56px; }
.section:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

.section-title {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  color: var(--text);
}

.section p, .section li { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; }
.section ul { padding-left: 20px; margin: 12px 0; }
.section li { margin-bottom: 6px; }

/* ── SCHEDULE CARDS ── */
.event-card {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 28px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
}
.event-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
.event-date {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.event-name {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.event-meta {
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px;
  font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.event-meta span { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; }
.event-description { font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.75; color: #444; }

/* ── STORY ── */
.story-photo {
  width: 100%;
  border-radius: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  object-fit: cover;
  max-height: 500px;
}

/* ── HOTEL CARDS ── */
.hotel-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 20px;
}
.hotel-card {
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 24px;
  transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
}
.hotel-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
.hotel-card h3 { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.hotel-badge {
  display: inline-block;
  background: #e8f5e9; color: #2e7d32;
  font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;
  padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

/* ── FAQ ── */
.faq-item {
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 20px 0;
}
.faq-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.faq-q {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  cursor: pointer;
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
}
.faq-q::after { content: '+'; font-size: 1.4rem; color: #999; transition: 0.2s; }
.faq-item.open .faq-q::after { content: '−'; }
.faq-a {
  max-height: 0; overflow: hidden;
  transition: max-height 0.3s ease;
  color: #555; line-height: 1.75;
}
.faq-item.open .faq-a { max-height: 600px; }

/* ── THINGS TO DO ── */
.category { margin-bottom: 40px; }
.category h3 {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
  padding-bottom: 8px;
  border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
}
.place { margin-bottom: 12px; }
.place strong { color: var(--text); }

/* ── BUTTONS ── */
.btn {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 14px 36px;
  border-radius: var(--button-radius);
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  cursor: pointer; border: none;
}
.btn-primary {
  background: var(--text);
  color: #fff;
}
.btn-primary:hover { background: #333; text-decoration: none; }
.btn-outline {
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--text);
  border: 2px solid var(--text);
}
.btn-outline:hover { background: var(--text); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; }
.btn-white {
  background: #fff;
  color: var(--text);
}
.btn-white:hover { background: #f0f0f0; text-decoration: none; }

/* ── FOOTER ── */
.site-footer {
  position: fixed; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 12px 24px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 20px;
}
.footer-date { font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem; }

/* ── REGISTRY ── */
.registry-message {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  padding: 60px 0;
  line-height: 1.8;
}
.registry-photo {
  border-radius: 12px;
  max-width: 500px;
  margin: 0 auto 40px;
}

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .hero { height: 70vh; min-height: 400px; }
  .page-hero { height: 35vh; min-height: 240px; }
  .content { padding: 40px 18px 120px; }
  .event-meta { flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .hotel-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .nav-menu {
    position: static; width: auto; height: auto;
    display: flex; border: none;
    background: transparent; padding: 0;
  }
  .nav-menu li a { padding: 8px 16px; }
  .hamburger { display: none; }
  .nav-overlay { display: none !important; }
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="site-header">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="index.html" class="nav-logo">Justin &amp; Jen</a>
    <button class="hamburger" aria-label="Menu">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
    <ul class="nav-menu">
      <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="schedule.html">Schedule</a></li>
      <li><a href="story.html">Story</a></li>
      <li><a href="travel.html">Travel</a></li>
      <li><a href="accommodations.html">Where to Stay</a></li>
      <li><a href="things-to-do.html">Things to Do</a></li>
      <li><a href="faq.html">Q &amp; A</a></li>
      <li><a href="registry.html">Registry</a></li>
      <li><a href="beach-day.html">Beach Day</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</header>
<div class="nav-overlay"></div>

<section class="page-hero">
  <img class="hero-img" src="cid:images-couple-story-webp@mhtml.blink" alt="Justin and Jen">
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <h1>Q &amp; A</h1>
</section>

<main class="content">

  <div class="section">
    <p>For all our friends and family who have lots of questions, please check out our Q &amp; A first!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item open">
    <div class="faq-q">When is the RSVP deadline?</div>
    <div class="faq-a">
      <p>Please RSVP by <strong>June 15th</strong>, so we can have an accurate headcount. :)</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-q">Can I bring a date?</div>
    <div class="faq-a">
      <p>Please check your invite for your +1 or ask one of us!</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-q">What should I wear?</div>
    <div class="faq-a">
      <p><strong>Island Formal / Aloha Formal attire.</strong></p>
      <p><strong>Women:</strong> Wear what makes you feel comfortable and confident! Leave heels at home due to terrain.</p>
      <p><strong>Men:</strong> Slacks, dress shoes, and either a dress shirt or a nice aloha shirt. Aloha shirts are considered formal wear here. Recommended brands: Reyn Spooner, Kahala, Sig Zane, or Tori Richards. Check Nordstrom Rack in Waikiki for deals.</p>
      <p>August in Hawai'i is hot! Wear breathable clothes, feel free to bring a hat.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-q">What is Shabbat and what is the Shabbat event?</div>
    <div class="faq-a">
      <p>Shabbat is a Jewish tradition of a Friday night dinner with family. We're hosting a casual picnic at Ala Moana Beach Park. All faiths welcome! No need to fly in early just for this.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-q">Where is the Beach Day and what should I bring?</div>
    <div class="faq-a">
      <p>Kailua Beach, where Jen and Justin live. More info under the <a href="beach-day.html">Beach Day</a> section.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-q">How do I get to the ceremony &amp; reception?</div>
    <div class="faq-a">
      <p>The ceremony is at Kualoa Ranch. We'll have shuttle buses from Waikiki. Parking is also available at the venue for those who drive.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</main>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <span class="footer-date">August 30th, 2026</span>
  <a href="https://withjoy.com/justinandjen/rsvp" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding:10px 28px;font-size:0.85rem;">RSVP</a>
</footer>

<script>
// Mobile navigation
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
  const hamburger = document.querySelector('.hamburger');
  const navMenu = document.querySelector('.nav-menu');
  const overlay = document.querySelector('.nav-overlay');

  if (hamburger) {
    hamburger.addEventListener('click', () => {
      hamburger.classList.toggle('active');
      navMenu.classList.toggle('open');
      overlay.classList.toggle('show');
    });
  }

  if (overlay) {
    overlay.addEventListener('click', () => {
      hamburger.classList.remove('active');
      navMenu.classList.remove('open');
      overlay.classList.remove('show');
    });
  }

  // FAQ accordion
  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-q').forEach(q => {
    q.addEventListener('click', () => {
      q.parentElement.classList.toggle('open');
    });
  });

  // Highlight active nav link
  const currentPage = window.location.pathname.split('/').pop() || 'index.html';
  document.querySelectorAll('.nav-menu a').forEach(link => {
    if (link.getAttribute('href') === currentPage) {
      link.classList.add('active');
    }
  });
});

</script>
</body>
</html>


